text: Jackie Biskupski (born January 11, 1966) is an American Democratic politician. She was the Mayor of Salt Lake City, Utah. She is the city's first openly gay mayor, and the second female mayor (after Deedee Corradini). She is a former member of the Utah House of Representatives, representing the 30th District in Salt Lake County from 1999 to 2011. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Mayors of Salt Lake City Category:Lesbians Category:American LGBT politicians Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
